targets.query:
from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "gps")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "gps_position")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude" or r["_field"] == "longitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "lap_times")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "best_lap_number" or r["_field"] == "best_time" or r["_field"] == "lap_counter" or r["_field"] == "last_time")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap_time"] == "best" or r["lap_time"] == "best_lap_number" or r["lap_time"] == "lap_number" or r["lap_time"] == "last")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "gps")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "total2")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "km_driven")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "forcex" or r["_measurement"] == "forcey")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "lap_number" or r["_field"] == "mean_force_x" or r["_field"] == "mean_force_y")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y")

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "spd")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["avg"] == "speed")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "lap_number" or r["_field"] == "mean_speed")

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "spd")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Record"] == "velocity")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "speed")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "acc")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y" or r["axis"] == "z")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "acc_x" or r["_field"] == "acc_y" or r["_field"] == "acc_z")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "vel_acc")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "vel_x" or r["_field"] == "vel_y" or r["_field"] == "vel_z")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y" or r["axis"] == "z")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "gyro")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "gyro_x" or r["_field"] == "gyro_y" or r["_field"] == "gyro_z")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y" or r["axis"] == "z")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "in" or r["_field"] == "out")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "angular_acc")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "ang_acc_x" or r["_field"] == "ang_acc_y" or r["_field"] == "ang_acc_z")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y" or r["axis"] == "z")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "delta")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "angles")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "pitch_angle" or r["_field"] == "roll_angle" or r["_field"] == "yaw_angle")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["axis"] == "x" or r["axis"] == "y" or r["axis"] == "z")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "in_delta7" or r["_field"] == "out_delta7")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "lap_times")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "lap_duration")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap"] == "duration")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "lap_times")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "time_loss2")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap_time"] == "loss")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)
